{
  "id": "663af10b942fc6001ca77f87",
  "title": "毀誉褒貶",
  "created": 1715138829,
  "updated": 1715179505,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "663af10b942fc6001ca77f87",
      "text": "毀誉褒貶",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1715138829,
      "updated": 1715138829
    },
    {
      "id": "663af10c1280f000007d50d4",
      "text": "[きよほうへん]と読む",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1715138829,
      "updated": 1715138841
    },
    {
      "id": "663b8fc4e5172d0000c29937",
      "text": " へん…！[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1715179461,
      "updated": 1715179465
    },
    {
      "id": "663af6fbbe12ad0000ce8526",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6011af6ec190410022be12ad",
      "created": 1715140348,
      "updated": 1715140348
    },
    {
      "id": "663af6fbbe12ad0000ce8527",
      "text": ">「毀誉褒貶」は「毀誉」と「褒貶」に分けることができます。「[毀誉]」は「誹謗と称賛」という意味。「[毀]」は「そしる」、「[誉]」は「良い評価」を表す字。また、「毀誉」だけでも言葉が成り立ちます。そして、「[褒貶]」は「褒めたり貶したりすること」",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1715140348,
      "updated": 1715179505
    },
    {
      "id": "663af733be12ad0000ce852e",
      "text": "「毀誉褒貶の激しい」",
      "userId": "6011af6ec190410022be12ad",
      "created": 1715140404,
      "updated": 1715140406
    },
    {
      "id": "663af736be12ad0000ce8530",
      "text": "「毀誉褒貶相半ば」",
      "userId": "6011af6ec190410022be12ad",
      "created": 1715140406,
      "updated": 1715140408
    },
    {
      "id": "663af738be12ad0000ce8531",
      "text": "「毀誉褒貶を顧みない」",
      "userId": "6011af6ec190410022be12ad",
      "created": 1715140408,
      "updated": 1715140412
    },
    {
      "id": "663af733be12ad0000ce852f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6011af6ec190410022be12ad",
      "created": 1715140404,
      "updated": 1715140404
    },
    {
      "id": "663af709be12ad0000ce852a",
      "text": ">身は毀誉褒貶の間にあるも心は水の如く",
      "userId": "6011af6ec190410022be12ad",
      "created": 1715140362,
      "updated": 1715140420
    },
    {
      "id": "663af71fbe12ad0000ce852d",
      "text": "名軍師黒田官兵衛が言ったとされるらしい言葉",
      "userId": "6011af6ec190410022be12ad",
      "created": 1715140384,
      "updated": 1715140423
    },
    {
      "id": "663af711be12ad0000ce852c",
      "text": "「世間の人からどのように言われようとも、我が心は水のように澄んでいる」という意味。官兵衛は後年、「如水」と名を改めることに。その名前の由来を「身は毀誉褒貶の間にあるも心は水の如く」と説明したとされています。",
      "userId": "6011af6ec190410022be12ad",
      "created": 1715140369,
      "updated": 1715140382
    },
    {
      "id": "663af70abe12ad0000ce852b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6011af6ec190410022be12ad",
      "created": 1715140362,
      "updated": 1715140362
    },
    {
      "id": "663af763be12ad0000ce8533",
      "text": "[賛否両論]",
      "userId": "6011af6ec190410022be12ad",
      "created": 1715140451,
      "updated": 1715140454
    },
    {
      "id": "663af763be12ad0000ce8534",
      "text": "[甲論乙駁]（こうろんおつばく）",
      "userId": "6011af6ec190410022be12ad",
      "created": 1715140451,
      "updated": 1715140481
    }
  ]
}